{
  "texts": [
    "Another application of MADDPG was presented by Qie et al. (2019), who developed a simultaneous target assignment and path planning algorithm based on MADDPG.",
    "They combined target assignment rewards with path planning rewards to find the shortest distance while ensuring collision avoidance.",
    "This centralized training and decentralized execution framework can also be employed in other algorithms as well.",
    "For example, He et al. (2021) utilized asynchronous multithreading in PPO (AMPPO) for underwater unmanned vehicles application.",
    "Another notably studied policy-gradient approach is PPO-based algorithms."
  ]
}